The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Business | On the move
                                                                                                                           6                                                                                      On the move
                                      
	Hikmet Ersek        
	Has taken over as president and chief executive officer of Western Union.                        
	Gaurang Pandya         
	Has been appointed managing director of Carrier India.                        
	Ameera Patel         
	Is the new chief executive officer of Metropolis Healthcare.                          
	Biswadip Mitra  
	Has been elected chairman of India Semiconductor Association.                        
	Geetika Saigal         
	has taken over as director for enterprise sales in India, Cable amp; Wireless Worldwide.              
	N. Raja         
	Has joined Ford India as vice-president of sales.              
	Rahul Singh        
	Has been appointed president (business services) of HCL Technologies.              
	Peter Martin        
	Is the new head of resort operations, Mahindra Holidays and Resorts India Limited.              
	John Ellingboe        
	Has been appointed senior vice-president, Discovery Chemistry.                                                                                                                                      
